%3E%3Cstrong%3E%5C%5C%3C%2Fstrong%3EMichael%20Biercuk%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Australian%20quantum%20infrastructure%20software%20company%20Q-CTRL%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20some%20of%20the%20earliest%20applications%20for%20quantum%20computing%20are%20%26quot%3Bjust%20not%20very%20sexy%2C%20but%20they%20are%20economically%2C%20extremely%20high%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20with%20over%20a%20dozen%20people%20in%20the%20quantum%20computing%20field%2C%20including%20researchers%20from%20IBM%20and%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20the%20executives%20behind%20startups%20including%20Q-CTRL%20and%20QuamCore%2C%20and%20scholars%20running%20some%20of%20the%20top%20quantum%20labs%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20they%20say%20are%20the%20most%20promising%20ways%20quantum%20computing%20could%20change%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247beb3fc-6d68-4e45-8561-dd86a7325d9e%5C%22%3EImproved%20logistics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20major%20opportunity%20for%20true%20quantum%20advantage%20is%20logistics%20optimization%20and%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20Bieruck%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20very%20challenging%20problems%2C%20and%20we%20know%20they%20are%20computationally%20bottlenecked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptimizing%20supply%20chains%20and%20improving%20logistics%20operations%20can%20make%20major%20organizations%20like%20the%20military%20and%20global%20shipping%20industry%20more%20efficient%2C%20helping%20businesses%20ensure%20consistent%20quality%20and%20reliable%20supply.%20This%20could%20also%20drive%20down%20the%20cost%20of%20consumer%20goods%2C%20reduce%20waste%2C%20and%20prevent%20spoilage%20of%20perishable%20items%2C%20potentially%20addressing%20larger%20social%20problems%20like%20world%20hunger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abf558a7-8480-4927-bfbf-53703e8a6bb4%5C%22%3ENew%20building%20materials%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELighter%20and%20more%20durable%20materials%20used%20to%20create%20