sinsider.com%2Fus-shipbuilding-problems-could-be-navys-achilles-heel-china-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewoes%20facing%20US%20shipbuilders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20smaller%20industrial%20base%20and%20erratic%20demand%20signals%20from%20the%20Navy%2C%20and%20how%20these%20long-standing%20challenges%20are%20affecting%20top%20Navy%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20say%20this%20plainly%2C%20we%20must%20act%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sen.%20Trent%20Kelly%2C%20the%20subcommittee%20chairman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20through%20changes%20to%20our%20procurement%20processes%2C%20stronger%20industrial%20base%20investments%2C%20or%20cultural%20shifts%20within%20shipbuilding%20program%20offices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Mississippi%20Republican%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20need%20to%20make%20these%20decisions%20sooner%20rather%20than%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20range%20of%20topics%20were%20discussed%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%20but%20the%20problems%20relating%20to%20shipbuilding%20workers%20were%20center%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consensus%20among%20witnesses%20like%20Eric%20Labs%2C%20senior%20analyst%20for%20naval%20forces%20and%20weapons%20with%20the%20Congressional%20Budget%20Office%2C%20and%20Shelby%20Oakley%2C%20the%20director%20of%20contracting%20and%20national%20security%20acquisitions%20with%20the%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%2C%20was%20that%20the%20starting%20point%20for%20fixing%20US%20shipbuilding%20issues%20is%20investing%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224922%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20of%20the%20USS%20John%20C.%20Stennis%20(CVN%2074)%20aircraft%20carrier%20is%20seen%2C%20with%20two%20smaller%20boats%20on%20its%20sides.%20The%20carrier%20sits%20in%20blue%20water%20with%20a%20blue%2C%20somewhat%20cloudy%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8a0e3b8b41a9673f9c561%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20heig