20invest%20in%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOakley's%20statement%20to%20lawmakers%20this%20week%2C%20which%20featured%20information%20from%20the%20GAO's%20study%20on%20Navy%20shipbuilding%2C%20said%20that%20shipyards%20are%20largely%20struggling%20to%20replace%20the%20loss%20of%20experienced%2C%20skilled%20workers%20with%20new%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20applies%2C%20too%2C%20to%20white-collar%20shipbuilders%20like%20designers%2C%20naval%20architects%2C%20and%20engineers%20who%20%26quot%3Bcan%20take%20other%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Ronald%20O'Rourke%2C%20a%20naval%20affairs%20analyst%20with%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20overlap%20with%20maintenance%20and%20repair%20yards.%20Oakley%20noted%20that%20the%20Navy's%20strategy%20has%20to%20focus%20on%20that%20alongside%20building%2C%20as%20they're%20inseparable%20and%20face%20similar%20issues%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224948%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20warships%2C%20and%20fighter%20jets%20are%20located%20in%20the%20blue%20waters%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723a5179b3250dbbceb6cbb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222907%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina's%20shipbuilding%20empire%20pumps%20out%20new%20warships%20at%20breakneck%20paces.%3Cp%3EPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20major%20US%20shipbuilders%2C%20especially%20those%20working%20on%20top%20US%20Navy%20submarines%20and%20surface%20ships%2C%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustry-knows-how-to-build-warships-navy-shipbuilding-insider-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferences%20between%20their%20workforces%20today%20and%2030%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20they're%20having%20trouble%20hiring%20people%20and%20k