theory%20and%20asset%20pricing%20for%20over%20five%20decades%20while%20taking%20his%20research%20to%20the%20real%20world%20by%20working%20with%20investors%20like%20David%20Booth%2C%20who%20was%20once%20his%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooth%2C%20now%20the%20chairman%20of%20Dimensional%20Fund%20Advisors%2C%20a%20firm%20with%20%24777%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management%20and%20over%20four%20decades%20of%20experience%2C%20shared%20that%20journey%20in%20a%20documentary%20with%20his%20mentor%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DT98825bzcKw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETune%20Out%20the%20Noise%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20reflects%20on%20how%20research%20by%20a%20group%20of%20academics%20and%20practitioners%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20in%20the%201960s%20challenged%20Wall%20Street's%20approach%20to%20investing.%20The%20documentary%20includes%20other%20notable%20Nobel%20Prize-winning%20economists%20with%20ties%20to%20the%20firm%2C%20including%20Robert%20Merton%20and%20Myron%20Scholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20an%20interview%20with%20Booth%20that%20discusses%20his%20journey%20including%20his%20thoughts%20on%20current%20market%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%3A%20In%20the%20film%2C%20you%20made%20a%20statement%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20predict%20the%20future%2C%20but%20focus%20instead%20on%20what%20can%20happen%2C%20which%20is%20a%20way%20to%20say%2C%20don't%20look%20at%20the%20bad%2C%20look%20at%20the%20good%20possibilities.%20What%20do%20you%20think%20can%20happen%20in%20markets%20today%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Booth%3A%20Individual%20stocks%2C%20as%20we%20all%20know%2C%20can%20go%20to%20zero%3B%20you%20can%20lose%20100%25%2C%20but%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20lose%20100%25%20in%20the%20market.%20And%20in%20the%20worst%20of%20times%20in%20the%20depression%2C%20the%20market%20was%20down%20about%2040%25%2C%20which%20is%20pretty%20tough%20to%20deal%20with%2C%20but%20that's%20why%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20put%20all%20your%20money%20in%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20half%20your%20money%20in%20stocks%20and%20the%20market%20is%20down%2040%25%2C%20then%20you're%20down%2020%25.%20So%20it's%20all%20about%20trying%20to%20manage%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20markets%20by%20controlling%20what%20percentage%20you%20have%20in%20stocks.%20And%20if%20you%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%20about%20stocks%2C%20then%20you%20may%20want%20to%20trim%20back%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20recommend%20planning%20around%20short-term%20moves%3B%20there's%20just%20no%20evidence%20that%20that%20really%20works.%20So%20what%20we%20mean%20by%20planning%20is%20you%20have%20a%20view%20of%20markets%20and%20how%20they%20work%2C%20and%20you%20come%20up%20with%20a%20sensible%20solution.%20And%20then%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%20is%20pay%20attention%20to%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20market%20and%20figure%20out%2C%20'Does%20this%20cause%20me%20to%20do%20anything%20differently%20based%20on%20what's%20happened%20at%20the%20market%20or%20what's%20happened%20in%20my%20personal%20life%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20'I%20won%20the%20lottery.%20Maybe%20I%20want%20to%20invest%20more%20in%20stock'.%20If%20I%20decide%20I'm%20going%20to%20retire%2C%20maybe%20you%20want%20to%20cut%20back.%20That%20sort%20of%20thing.%20So%20pay%20attention%20to%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20the%20market.%20That's%20what%20I%20mean%20by%20planning.%20Don't%20try%20to%20predict%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20market.%20It's%20like%20life.%20Few%20of%20us%20could%20have%20predicted%2020%20years%20ago%20where%20we'd%20be%20today.%20But%20somewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20we%20adapted%2C%20and%20as%20we%20developed%20a%20plan%2C%20we%20realized%20we%20had%20to%20adapt%20to%20whatever%20was%20going%20on%20and%20figure%20out%20a%20new%20path%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20current%20trade%20wars%20seem%20to%20have%20no%20end.%20We%20are%20seeing%20tariff%20threats%20and%20then%20counter-tariff%20threats%20and%20then%20counter%2C%20counter-tariff%20threats.%20How%20do%20you%20navigate%20that%20in%20the%20market%3F%20Is%20that%20just%20noise%2C%20or%20are%20there%20considerations%20that%20investors%20need%20to%20take%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooth%3A%20The%20market%20seems%20to%20say%2C%20'Whatever%20is%20going%20on%20is%20not%20very%20good%20for%20stocks'.%20But%20you%20can't%20take%20that%20information%20and%20say%2C%20'okay%2C%20well%2C%20I%20think%20I'll%20get%20out%20of%20the%20market'.%20Because%20the%20market%20has%20already%20reacted.%20Unless%20you%20know%20more%20than%20the%20market%2C%20I%20think%20you%20have%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20say%2C%20'Look%2C%20government%20actions%20cause%20prices%20to%20move'%2C%20but%20unless%20you're%20faster%20and%20smarter%20than%20everybody%20else%2C%20there's%20not%20much%20you%20can%20do%20about%20it%20except%20look%20at%20the%20outcome%20and%20say%2C%20'Okay%2C%20based%20on%20what's%20happened%2C%20is%20there%20anything%20I%20should%20do%20differently%3F'%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20there%20may%20be%20good%20reasons%20to%20do%20something%20differently%2C%20but%20not%20trying%20to%20time%20the%20market.%20You%20may%20want%20to%20do%20things%20differently%20because%20with%20less%20money%20in%20your%20pocket%2C%20maybe%20there%20are%20some%20things%20you%20don't%20buy%20that%20you're%20thinking%20about%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20is%20the%20biggest%20mistake%20you%20see%20investors%20making%20today%20in%20markets%2C%20whether%20it's%20on%20the%20institutional%20or%20the%20retail%20side%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooth%3A%20Well%2C%20in%20both%2C%20there's%20a%20similar%20problem%2C%20which%20is%20really%20hitting%20us%20hard%20right%20now%2C%20which%20is%20just%20anxiety.%20Anytime%20there's%20a%20spike%20up%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20it%20creates%20more%20anxiety.%20We%20do%20have%20an%20objective%20measure%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20which%20is%20the%20VIX%20index%2C%20which%20has%20spiked%20up%20recently%2C%20and%20when%20that%20happens%2C%20frequently%2C%20stocks%20decline%2C%20and%20anxiety%20levels%20go%20up.%20And%20the%20worst%20mistake%20people%20make%20is%20to%20try%20to%20time%20short-term%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20like%20now%2C%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%2C%20and%20they%20go%2C%20'Oh%20man%2C%20I'm%20stressed%20out.%20I%20think%20I'll%20get%20out.'%20And%20then%20the%20market%20instead%20of%20going%20down%2C%20goes%20up%2C%20they%20go%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20can't%20get%20in%20now.%20The%20train%20has%20already%20left%20the%20station.'%20So%20it's%20that%20kind%20of%20behavior%20that%20we're%20trying%20to%20help%20people%20work%20through%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20have%20a%20good%20long-term%20investment%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20stated%20that%20the%20lower%20the%20price%20you%20pay%20for%20a%20stock%2C%20the%20better%20your%20return%20is.%20But%20the%20open-ended%20question%20is%2C%20lower%20price%20to%20what%3F%20What%20are%20some%20of%20the%20rules%20that%20you%20look%20at%20when%20you're%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20rightly%20priced%2C%20cheap%20stock%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooth%3A%20There's%20almost%20a%20whole%20industry%20in%20the%20academic%20world%20right%20now%20trying%20to%20research%20what%20is%20the%20best%20way%20of%20defining%20a%20low-price%20stock.%20And%20all%20of%20them%20are%20pretty%20good.%20None%20of%20them%20are%20perfect.%20Eugene%20Fama%20and%20Ken%20French%20have%20a%20tendency%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20use%3B%20we%20primarily%20focus%20on%20price%20relative%20to%20book%20value%2C%20but%20also%2C%20this%20low%20price%20shows%20up%20whether%20you%20do%20a%20price%20relative%20to%20dividends%20or%20price%20relative%20to%20earnings.%20Just%20in%20our%20view%2C%20scaling%20price%20by%20book%20value%20seems%20to%20work%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20like%20art.%20Do%20you%20pick%20your%20art%20like%20you%20pick%20your%20stocks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBooth%3A%20Well%2C%20I%20tend%20to%20gravitate%20toward%20minimal%20art.%20The%20thing%20about%20minimal%20art%20is%2C%20at%20first%2C%20you%20might%20think%2C%20'Gosh%2C%20I%20could%20have%20done%20that.%20That's%20just%20some%20squiggles'.%20Well%2C%20you%20couldn't.%20It's%20much%20more%20complex.%20And%20particularly%2C%20the%20large%20sculptures%20that%20I%20collect%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20engineering%20and%20structural%20work%20that%20has%20to%20go%20on.%20And%20so%20what%20comes%20out%20is%20something%20that%20looks%20pretty%20simple%2C%20but%20underneath%2C%20it%20was%20actually%20pretty%20complex.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20describes%20investing.%20We%20try%20to%20describe%20things%20in%20a%20simple%20way%2C%20but%20investing%20is%20not%20simple.%20It%20is%20complex.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20in%20our%20efforts%20to%20try%20to%20come%20up%20with%20sensible%2C%20simple%20ideas%2C%20people%20go%2C%20'Geez%2C%20that's%20too%20simple'.%20But%20underneath%20these%20ideas%2C%20there's%20just%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20research%20over%20the%20last%2060%20years%20by%20incredibly%20bright%20people%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20got%20Nobel%20Prizes.%20So%20if%20what%20we%20do%20kind%20of%20sounds%20simple%2C%20that's%20kind%20of%20what%20we're%20aiming%20for.%20But%20trust%20me%2C%20underneath%2C%20it's%20pretty%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-booth-interview-stock-market-investing-tips-buying-cheap-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742121001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d42ea869253ccddf994317%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22ht