%20about%20US%20stocks%20under%20Trump%20is%20John%20Stoltzfus%2C%20as%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oppenheimer.com%2Fnews-media%2F2024%2Finsights%2Foam%2Fjohn-stoltzfus-announces-7100-price-target.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%20price%20target%20of%207%2C100%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicates.%20Oppenheimer's%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20believes%20that%20this%20latest%20turbulence%20is%20caused%20by%20short-term-focused%20traders%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20shake%20out%20those%20with%20weak%20stomachs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20their%20game%3A%20they%20pick%20up%20on%20this%2C%20and%20they%20play%20bears%2C%20skeptics%2C%20and%20nervous%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Stoltzfus%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20get%20scared%3B%20they%20sell%20into%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-decade%20market%20veteran%20suggests%20that%20investors%20with%20a%20longer%20time%20horizon%20search%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20babies%20that%20get%20tossed%20out%20with%20the%20bathwater.%26quot%3B%20His%20favorite%20sectors%20are%20growth-heavy%20groups%20like%20%3Cstrong%3Etechnology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ecommunication%20services%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Econsumer%20discretionary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Eindustrials%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%2C%20like%20Blazek%20from%20Neuberger%20Berman%2C%20are%20less%20excited%20about%20growth-oriented%20sectors.%20The%20investment%20chief%20was%20wary%20of%20how%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20stocks%20dominated%2C%20and%20he%20now%20expects%20them%20to%20lag.%20That%20would%20be%20healthy%2C%20he%20said%2C%20though%20it%20may%20perpetuate%20the%20market%20reset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20sideways%20until%20we%20get%20clarity%2C%26quot%3B%20Blazek%20said%20of%20the%20stock%20market.%20%26quot%3BWe%20absolutely%20could%20see%20the%20stage%20set%20for%20regaining%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%