2C%20while%20he%20would%20rake%20in%20%24250%20for%20the%20same%20work.%20And%20since%20he%20often%20had%20more%20clients%20than%20I%20did%2C%20he%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20make%20much%20more%20than%20me.%20Most%20months%2C%20he%20would%20bring%20in%20more%20than%20five%20times%20what%20I%20made.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20wasn't%20something%20we%20openly%20discussed%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20it%20in%20every%20plan%2C%20discussion%2C%20purchase%2C%20and%20moment%20when%20I%20had%20to%20choose%20between%20admitting%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20something%20or%20pretending%20I%20could.%20I%20always%20chose%20the%20latter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20casually%20booked%20weekend%20getaways%2C%20I'd%20always%20suggest%20he%20make%20plans%20with%20his%20friends%20because%2C%20mentally%2C%20I%20was%20calculating%20how%20much%20I%20could%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-of-12-weekly-grocery-budget-meal-planning-recipes-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espend%20on%20groceries%20for%20the%20week%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20day%20he%20casually%20blew%20%24200%20on%20new%20shoes%2C%20I%20struggled%20to%20gather%20enough%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20my%20insurance%20before%20the%20deadline.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%2022%2C%20I%20was%20hustling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20saving%20every%20dollar%20I%20earned%20for%20tuition%20and%20the%20future%20I%20hoped%20we'd%20share%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ade5d27b-5ebc-4946-9644-3e338dcacce1%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20financial%20disparity%20took%20a%20huge%20toll%20on%20me%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20felt%20a%20silent%20pressure%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20him.%20He%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20gap%20between%20us%20but%20didn't%20know%20how%20much%20it%20affected%20me%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20spell%20it%20out.%20I%20felt%20guilty%20for%20n