ole%20industry%20stopped%2C%20but%20what%20do%20you%20recommend%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20you%20should%20try%20out%20voice%20acting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20hearing%20since%20I%20was%20young%20that%20I%20sounded%20like%20a%2040-year-old%20man.%20That%20has%20always%20been%20a%20head-turner%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20joke%20among%20friends%2C%20family%2C%20and%20on-set%20with%20casting%20directors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20met%20with%20a%20coach%20and%20spent%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20just%20taking%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20I%20started%20to%20take%20off%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram.%20By%20early%202023%2C%20I%20had%20found%20Quinn%2C%20an%20audio%20storytelling%20app.%20I%20started%20working%20with%20them%20in%202023%20and%20have%20been%20doing%20that%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0bce838-5f94-454a-b183-8159da7da599%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20refused%20to%20do%20an%20AI%20voice-over%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joined%20my%20former%20talent%20agency%20around%20March%202024%20but%20parted%20ways%20in%20February%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20agency%20sent%20me%20to%20an%20audition%20in%20February.%20For%20this%20specific%20job%2C%20I%20took%20a%20step%20back%20and%20read%20the%20email%2C%20which%20mentioned%20machine%20learning%2C%20synthesized%20voice%2C%20and%20text-to-speech.%20I%20saw%20that%20the%20payout%20was%20listed%20as%20up%20high%20five%20figures%2C%20low%20six%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20saw%20that%20AI%20was%20involved%2C%20I%20was%20skeptical.%20As%20I%20reviewed%20further%2C%20they%20were%20casting%20100%20people%2C%20and%20if%20I%20had%20submitted%20to%20the%20audition%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20in%20tandem%20with%20an%20NDA.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20if%20they%20took%20my%20voice%20and%20melded%20it%20with%2099%20other%20people%20or%20used%20only%20my%20voice%2C%20I%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20publicly%20say%20that's%20my%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20a%20huge%20red%20flag%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20problem%20with%20machine%20learning%20and%20generative%20AI%20is%20they%20can't%20get%20the%20voices%20right%20when%20they're%20developing%20full%20movies%20or%20TV%20shows.%20So%2C%20to%20me%2C%20this%20project%20is%20what%20some%20companies%20are%20doing%20in%20response%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20my%20agency%20I%20didn't%20feel%20comfortable%20doing%20this%20job.%20It's%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20money%2C%20and%20that%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20me.%20I%20did%20not%20make%20anywhere%20near%20enough%20to%20scoff%20at%20a%20hundred%20thousand%20dollars%2C%20so%20it%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20they%20said%20this%20may%20not%20be%20the%20agency%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20understood%20in%20that%20moment.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20You're%20right.%20Maybe%20I'm%20not%20a%20good%20fit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20still%20agentless%2C%20but%20I%20do%20have%20a%20manager%20now.%20I%20just%20signed%20with%20a%20big%20voice%20acting%20company%20early%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da8d714e-c2c5-41a7-8d34-451dfb26442c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EActors%20are%20learning%20to%20navigate%20AI%20jobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20casual%20conversations%20with%20colleagues%20and%20friends%2C%20some%20actors%20accept%20the%20inevitability%20%E2%80%94%20or%20at%20least%20believe%20in%20the%20inevitability%20%E2%80%94%20that%20there%20will%20come%20a%20time%20when%20actors%20will%20be%20auditioning%20against%20audio-generated%20voices.%20It%20adds%20a%20level%20of%20hopelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20the%20average%20voice%20actor%20is%20doing%20everything%20they%20can%20to%20stay%20far%20away%20from%20companies%20using%20AI%2C%20and%20they're%20doing%20the