%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20has%20%26quot%3Brapidly%20established%20a%20reliable%20supply%20chain%2C%20recently%20securing%20contracts%20for%20all%20long-lead%20components%20needed%20for%20construction%2C%20and%20today%20announced%20an%20agreement%20to%20establish%20a%20manufacturing%20supply%20chain%20to%20assist%20in%20the%20development%20of%20multiple%20reactors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20actively%20constructing%20the%20non-nuclear%20portions%20of%20the%20Natrium%20commercial%20demonstration%20plant%20in%20Kemmerer%2C%20Wyoming%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20the%20US%20Nuclear%20Regulatory%20Commission%20recently%20announced%20that%20our%20safety%20evaluation%20is%20ahead%20of%20schedule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20a%20deal%20with%20Sabey%20Data%20Centers%20to%20explore%20deployment%20opportunities%20for%20its%20Natrium%20reactors%20in%20the%20Rocky%20Mountain%20region%20and%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a654a06-0ea3-4110-a385-7edfd1fa935c%5C%22%3ENewcleo%2C%20%24585M%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewcleo-coo-nuclear-startup-europe-small-modular-reactor-ipo-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENewcleo%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20new%20player%20in%20the%20reactor%20field%20that%20launched%20in%202021%20and%20is%20based%20in%20Paris.%20It%20was%20founded%20by%20Italian%20physicist%20Stefano%20Buono%2C%20an%20alum%20of%20the%20European%20Organization%20for%20Nuclear%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20specializes%20in%20lead-cooled%20fast%20reactors%2C%20which%20use%20liquid%20or%20molten%20lead%20as%20a%20coolant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20design%20that%20was%20actually%20demonstrated%20by%20the%20Russians%20on%20some%20of%20their%20submarines%20back%20in%20the%20'70s%2C%26quot%3B%20Buongiorno%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%20nothing%20is%20entirely%20new%20here%2C%20my%20friend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewcleo%20said%20in%20February%20that%20it%20started%20the%20land%20acquisition%20process%20to%20build%20its%20first%20lead-cooled%20fast%20reactor%20in%20France%20by%202031.%20It%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20demonstrator%20reactor%2C%20showcasing%20the%20viability%20of%20the%20SMR%20design%2C%20according%20to%20a%20company%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Newcleo%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bbenefits%20from%20strong%20public%20recognition%20and%20support%20both%20in%20France%20and%20across%20Europe%20and%20is%20one%20of%20only%20two%20Advanced%20Modular%20Reactor%20projects%20selected%20by%20the%20European%20Industrial%20Alliance%20on%20Small%20Modular%20Reactors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282923b8b-57ab-48a8-b115-284b917de788%5C%22%3ENuScale%20Power%2C%20%24468.7M%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENuScale%20was%20founded%20in%20Corvallis%2C%20Oregon%2C%20in%202007%20by%20Jos%C3%A9%20Reyes%2C%20a%20fellow%20of%20the%20American%20Nuclear%20Society%2C%20and%20Paul%20Lorenzini%2C%20former%20CEO%20of%20Powercor%20Australia%20electric%20provider.%20The%20company%20went%20public%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuScale's%20SMR%20designs%20are%20based%20on%20the%20more%20common%20light-water%20reactor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20kind%20of%20simplifying%2C%20but%20it%20is%20essentially%20a%20smaller%20version%20of%20large%20pressurized%20water%20reactors%2C%20which%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20nuclear%20industry%20as%20we%20have%20known%20it%20for%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Buongiorno%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuScale%20CEO%20John%20L.%20Hopkins%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20call%20on%20March%203%20that%20light-water%20SMRs%20give%20NuScale%20an%20edge%20over%20others%20in%20the%20SMR%20space%20because%20they're%20%26quot%3Bnot%20burdened%20by%20the%20additional%20hurdles%20faced%20by%20non-light%20water%20reactor%20SMR%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20NuScale%20has%20not%20been%20without%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20company%20has%20agreements%20to%20develop%20SMRs%20in%20Ghana%2C%20Romania%2C%20and%20Poland%2C%20NuScale%20has%20yet%20to%20ink%20a%20deal%20to%20develop%20one%20of%20its%20reactors%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlans%20to%20build%20six%20of%20NuScale's%2077-megawatt%20reactors%20in%20Idaho%20were%20terminated%20in%202023%20because%20the%20project%20failed%20to%20attract%20enough%20customers%20to%20support%20soaring%20costs%20stemming%20from%20inflation%2C%20Hopkins%20said%20during%20an%20earnings%20call%20in%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20presentation%20that%20NuScale%20has%20seen%20increased%20interest%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20an%20era%20where%20more%20energy%20is%20necessary%20to%20fortify%20the%20US%20electricity%20grid%2C%20power%20economic%20growth%2C%20and%20bolster%20America's%20global%20competitiveness%2C%20the%20need%20for%20new%20nuclear%20is%20becoming%20a%20reality%2C%26quot%3B%20Hopkins%20said%20during%20the%20fourth-quarter%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-modular-reactor-venture-capital-ai-data-centers-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742116801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d0b7fc69253ccddf98f21d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-modular-reactor-venture-capital-ai-data-centers-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Just%204%20small%20modular%20reactor%20companies%20have%20received%20%243B%20in%20VC%20funding.%20But%20leading%20experts%20tell%20BI%20it's%20unclear%20if%20SMRs%20will%20solve%20AI%20energy%20needs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-modular-reactor-venture-capital-ai-data-centers-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20how%20the%20'millionaire%20next%20door'%20is%20being%20advised%20to%20invest%20amid%20economic%20fears%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mansion%20with%20money.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d480bfb8b41a9673fabd28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EManuel%20Tsanoudakis%2FGetty%2C%20PNC%2FGetty%2C%20Marat%20Musabirov%2FiStock%2C%20Elena%20Frolova%2FiStock%2C%20Ava%20Horton%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWashington's%20tariff%20threats%20and%20global%20counter-responses%20are%20fueling%20market%20uncertainty%20and%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20face%20potential%20stagflation%2C%20prompting%20strategic%20asset%20allocation%20and%20cash%20management.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20advise%20cautious%20stock%20moves%2C%20favoring%20high-quality%20bonds%20and%20Big%20Tech%20for%20recovery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWashington's%20tariff%20threats%20are%20real%20but%20not%20the%20only%20problem%3A%20the%20continued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-escalates-trade-war-canada-increases-tarrifs-aluminum-steel-cars-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecounter-responses%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20other%20countries%20have%20turned%20this%20trade%20war%20into%20a%20vicious%20cycle%20that%20makes%20it%20hard%20for%20any%20seasoned%20economist%20to%20call%20the%20endpoint.%20And%20that%20type%20of%20ambiguity%20is%20making%20markets%20nervous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20reevaluation%20of%20risk%20and%20a%20sentiment%20shift%20to%20the%20downside%20for%20markets%2C%20said%20Jim%20Baird%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Plante%20Moran%20Financial%20Advisors.%20He%20services%20clients%20with%20net%20worths%20beginning%20at%20%24500%2C000%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bmillionaire-next-door%26quot%3B%20type.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20they%20aren't%20yet%20in%20the%20ultrawealthy%20range%20where%20they%20can%20sit%20a%20downturn%20out%20or%20resort%20to%20private%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-investment-apps-for-beginners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvestors%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20enough%20exposure%20to%20public%20markets%20that%20it%20could%20seriously%20impact%20their%20wealth.%20It's%20a%20predicament%20that%20has%20put%20money%20managers%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20rethinking%20their%20clients'%20exposures%20relative%20to%20their%20needs%20amid%20a%20rapidly%20shifting%20economic%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaird%20isn't%20expecting%20a%20near-term%20recession%20but%20is%20concerned%20about%20the%20risk%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstagflation-recession-us-economic-outlook-inflation-growth-unemployment-torsten-slok-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estagflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-february-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffebruary-jobs-report-unemployment-rate-employment-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunemployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20both%20remain%20high.%20For%20that%2C%20he's%20assessing%20whether%20clients%20have%20enough%20cash%20to%20cover%20their%20monthly%20needs%20and%20any%20big%20payments%20they%20may%20have%20coming%20up.%20This%20helps%20them%20avoid%20selling%20equities%20when%20the%20market%20is%20down.%20It's%20typically%20known%20as%20the%20emergency%20fund.%20But%20clients%20who%20are%20retired%20or%20nearing%20retirement%20should%20aim%20to%20have%20six%20to%2012%20months%20of%20their%20needs%20in%20cash.%20As%20for%20those%20who%20still%20have%20a%20wage%20and%20aren't%20worried%20about%20losing%20it%2C%20carrying%20too%20much%20cash%20doesn't%20make%20sense%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20coaching%20clients%20on%20strategic%20asset%20allocation%20while%20reviewing%20their%20portfolio%20positioning.%20When%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20volatile%2C%20it%20could%20be%20an%20opportunity%20to%20move%20some%20positions%20around%2C%20he%20noted.%20But%20those%20decisions%20would%20be%20made%20based%20on%20an%20individual%20client's%20needs.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20exposure%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-market-cap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20caps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20time%20to%20top%20that%20position%20while%20offloading%20other%20areas%20that%20could%20be%20used%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftaxes%2Ftax-loss-harvesting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax-loss-harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BComing%20off%20of%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20equity%20investors%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20done%20pretty%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Baird%20said.%20And%20so%20they%20may%20be%20in%20a%20decent%20position%20to%20reduce%20portfolio%20risk%20without%20risking%20their%20ability%20to%20meet%20their%20long-term%20goals%20and%20objectives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20don't%20want%20to%20take%20too%20much%20risk%20on%20stocks%20or%20are%20already%20dependent%20on%20their%20investment%20portfolio%2C%20he%20advises%20them%20to%20lean%20into%20high-quality%20bonds%20that%20still%20provide%20a%20good%20enough%20yield.%20But%20he%20doesn't%20suggest%20longer-duration%20bonds%20in%20case%20there's%20an%20uptick%20in%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKen%20Mahoney%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Mahoney%20Asset%20Management%2C%20advises%20those%20with%20net%20wealth%20between%20%241%20million%20to%20%24%2010%20million%20in%20assets.%20He%20has%20been%20helping%20clients%20trim%20some%20of%20their%20positions%20since%20late%20last%20year%20and%20into%202025.%20But%20not%20because%20of%20the%20trade%20wars%2C%20per%20se%3A%20He%20was%20concerned%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20hadn't%20seen%20a%20correction%20in%20some%20time%20and%20expected%20a%2010%25%20pullback%20at%20some%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20things%20look%20gloomy%20right%20now%2C%20he's%20also%20prepared%20for%20a%20large%20change%20in%20the%20president's%20tone%20and%20policy%20that%20could%20bring%20markets%20flying%20back.%20His%20strategy%20with%20clients%20has%20been%20to%20remain%20tactical%20while%20watching%20for%20positive%20signs%20of%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20feel%20like%20they%20missed%20the%20curve%20and%20the%20market%20has%20already%20turned%20for%20the%20worst%2C%20Mahoney%20says%20it's%20not%20too%20late.%20Investors%20can%20still%20make%20some%20tactical%20moves.%20Just%20see%20this%20as%20a%20time%20when%20the%20good%20stuff%20is%20on%20sale%20and%20go%20shopping%20for%20high-quality%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20expects%20a%20rally%20back%20into%20Big%20Tech%20stocks%20like%20Apple%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20when%20the%20market%20begins%20to%20recover%E2%80%94%20although%20he%20can't%20guarantee%20when%20that%20will%20happen.%20But%20since%20these%20names%20are%20the%20most%20liquid%20stocks%2C%20institutions%20will%20add%20them%20back%20into%20their%20portfolios%20as%20fast%20as%20they%20offloaded%20them%2C%20he%20said.%20These%20companies%20are%20also%20supported%20by%20strong%20fundamentals%2C%20big%20balance%20sheets%2C%20and%20hefty%20cash%2C%20and%20they%20remain%20key%20to%20long-term%20technological%20innovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20still%20risk%20in%20the%20market%2C%20which%20means%20sectors%20like%20small%20caps%20may%20not%20be%20the%20place%20to%20go%20looking%20for%20sales.%20Mahoney%20is%20only%20sticking%20to%20the%20Mag%207%20and%20potentially%20other%20stocks%20with%20relative%20balance%20sheet%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20growth%20managers%2C%20so%20that%20is%20where%20we%20will%20stay%20focused%20in%20looking%20to%20nibble%20at%20tech%2C%20and%20the%20key%20word%20there%20is%20nibble%20as%20this%20is%20not%20a%20place%20to%20get%20aggressive%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahoney%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20like%20to%20buy%20high%20and%20sell%20higher%20and%20buy%20confirmed%20strength%20more%20in%20the%20markets%20we%20had%20in%202023%20and%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20indexes%20start%20making%20higher%20lows%2C%20Mahoney%20would%20consider%20becoming%20slightly%20more%20aggressive%20because%20it's%20an%20early%20sign%20that%20the%20selling%20pressure%20is%20subsiding.%20Another%20sign%20he'll%20be%20looking%20for%20is%20the%20cooling%20off%20of%20the%20CBOE%20Volatility%20Index%2C%20a%20measure%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20expected%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20for%20investors%20looking%20for%20broader%20exposure%2C%20he%20suggests%20dollar-cost%20averaging%20%E2%80%94%20buying%20fixed%20amounts%20at%20regular%20intervals%20%E2%80%94%20into%20the%20indexes%20if%20they%20have%20time%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20market.%20That's%20because%20once%20we%20correct%2C%20you%20can%20gain%20an%20extra%2010%25%20from%20the%20reversal%2C%20Mahoney%20noted.%20And%20if%20we%20remain%20in%20freefall%2C%20that%20means%20more%20shares%20at%20a%20lower%20price%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20you'll%20want%20some%20cash%20or%20what%20Wall%20Street%20calls%20%26quot%3Bdry%20powder%26quot%3B%20to%20set%20aside%20so%20you%20can%20buy.%20He%20recommends%20keeping%20that%20cash%20in%20money%20markets%20that%20can%20be%20liquidated%20at%20the%20par%20value%20of%20%241%20at%20any%20point%2C%20making%20them%20a%20more%20flexible%20option%20over%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-millionaires-invest-stocks-bonds-financial-advice-economic-recession-fears-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742116441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d480bfb8b41a9673fabd28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-millionaires-invest-stocks-bonds-financial-advice-economic-recession-fears-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Explore%20strategic%20asset%20allocation%20and%20cash%20management%20advice%20for%20millionaires%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20recovery%20opportunities%20in%20stocks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmaidan%40businessinsider.com%20(Laila%20Maidan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-millionaires-invest-stocks-bonds-financial-advice-economic-recession-fears-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20says%20killed%20two%20Hezbollah%20militants%20in%20Lebanon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742116365000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119072374%2Cimgsize-728968.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-says-killed-two-hezbollah-militants-in-lebanon%2Farticleshow%2F119072241.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119072241.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20it%20killed%20two%20Hezbollah%20militants%20Sunday%20in%20two%20separate%20strikes%20on%20Lebanon%2C%20its%20latest%20deadly%20raids%20in%20the%20country%20more%20than%20three