-between-dad-pankaj-kapur-and-wife-mira-rajput%2Farticleshow%2F119070943.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpaceX%20Crew%20Dragon%20Docks%20With%20Space%20Station%20To%20Reach%20Sunita%20Williams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20pair%20of%20astronauts%20stranded%20for%20more%20than%20nine%20months%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20were%20a%20step%20closer%20to%20returning%20home%20Sunday%20after%20a%20replacement%20crew%20docked%20with%20the%20orbital%20outpost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronauts%20were%20shown%20on%20live%20TV%20embracing%20and%20hugging%20their%20counterparts%20in%20zero%20gravity%20on%20the%20space%20station%20shortly%20after%20their%20SpaceX%20Crew%20Dragon%20arrived%20at%200545%20GMT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EButch%20Wilmore%20and%20Suni%20Williams%20have%20been%20stuck%20aboard%20the%20ISS%20since%20June%20after%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20they%20were%20testing%20on%20its%20maiden%20crewed%20voyage%20suffered%20propulsion%20issues%20and%20was%20deemed%20unfit%20to%20fly%20them%20back%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliam%20said%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bwonderful%20day%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20to%20see%20our%20friends%20arrive%2C%26quot%3B%20speaking%20shortly%20after%20her%20colleges%20emerged%20onto%20the%20orbital%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20posted%20online%20by%20NASA%20astronaut%20Don%20Pettit%20showed%20the%20Crew%20Dragon%20vehicle%20approaching%20the%20ISS%20as%20it%20orbited%20the%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NASA%20duo's%20Starliner%20had%20returned%20to%20Earth%20empty%2C%20without%20experiencing%20further%20major%20issues%20--%20leaving%20them%20stuck%20for%20nine%20months%20after%20what%20was%20meant%20to%20have%20been%20a%20days-long%20roundtrip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20prolonged%20stay%20was%20significantly%20longer%20than%20the%20standard%20ISS%20rotation%20for%20astronauts%20of%20roughly%20six%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E