al%20family%20of%20Mewar%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20HRH%20group%20of%20hotels%20died%20early%20Sunday%20in%20Udaipur%20after%20prolonged%20illness%2C%20family%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMewar%20(81)%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Rajput%20king%20Maharana%20Pratap%2C%20was%20ill%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20under%20treatment%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20City%20Palace%20in%20Udaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20survived%20by%20wife%20Vijayraj%20Kumari%2C%20son%20Lakshyaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%20and%20daughters%20Bhargavi%20Kumari%20Mewar%20and%20Padmaja%20Kumari%20Parmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20funeral%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20mark%20of%20respect%2C%20the%20Udaipur%20City%20Palace%20will%20be%20closed%20for%20tourists%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday%20He%20was%20the%20younger%20son%20of%20Bhagwant%20Singh%20Mewar%20and%20Sushila%20Kumari.%20His%20elder%20brother%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Mewar%20died%20in%20November%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Singh%20Mewar%20was%20educated%20at%20the%20prestigious%20Mayo%20College%2C%20Ajmer%20and%20pursued%20hotel%20management%20courses%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20US.%20He%20received%20training%20in%20various%20international%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20lived%20and%20worked%20in%20Chicago%20for%20many%20years%20before%20building%20the%20HRH%20group%20of%20hotels%20as%20a%20professionally-managed%20corporate%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20avid%20cricketer%2C%20Mewar%20made%20his%20debut%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy%20as%20Rajasthan's%20skipper%20in%201945-46%20and%20had%20an%20eventful%20career%20for%20almost%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20a%20polo-player%20in%20the%201970s%20before%20he%20gave%20up%20the%20sport%20due%20to%20medical%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20showcase%20his%20commitment%20to%20professional%20polo%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20he%20instituted%20'The%20Udaipur%20Cup'%20at%20the%20Cambridge%20and%20Newmarket%20Polo%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Udaipur%2C%20Mewar%20Polo%20was%20formed%20as%20a%20polo%20team%20with%20professional%20players%20who%20had%20been%20handpicked%20and%20specially%20trained%20for%20Indian%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mewar%20Polo%20team%20lifted%20the%20prestigious%20President's%20Cup%20defeating%20the%2061st%20Cavalry%20players%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20an%20avid%20pilot%20and%20has%20done%20solo%20flights%20across%20India%20in%20a%20microlite%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMewar%20was%20the%20Chairman%20and%20Managing%20Trustee%20of%20the%20Maharana%20of%20Mewar%20Charitable%20Foundation%2C%20Udaipur.%20He%20also%20headed%20other%20trusts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%20Bhagwat%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20there%20have%20been%20conflicts%20and%20issues%20between%20his%20descendants%20regarding%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20house%20of%20Mewar%20and%20a%20property%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagwant%20Singh%20willed%20his%20property%20through%20a%20trust%20to%20Arvind%2C%20named%20him%20his%20successor%2C%20and%20disinherited%20his%20eldest%20son%2C%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20because%20he%20had%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%20in%201984%2C%20Arvind%20assumed%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20house.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20being%20the%20elder%20son%2C%20was%20coronated%20as%20the%20titular%20head%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahendra%20Singh%20Mewar%20died%20in%20November%20last%20year%20and%20his%20son%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20Mewar%2C%20also%20a%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20was%20made%20the%20titular%20head%20of%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20Vishvaraj%20Singh%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20City%20Palace%20of%20Udaipur%20by%20his%20cousin%20brother%20and%20Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar's%20son%20Lakshyaraj%20Singh%20to%20complete%20the%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20deadlock%20ended%20later%20after%20Vishwaraj%20Singh%20was%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20city%20Palace%20to%20visit%20'dhuni'%20(sacred%20fire)%20to%20offer%20prayers%20to%20the%20deity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742108760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1n2klea8_arvind-_625x300_16_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharana-prataps-descendant-royal-family-member-arvind-singh-mewar-dies-7934593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Singh%20Mewar%20(81)%2C%20a%20descendant%20of%20Rajput%20king%20Maharana%20Pratap%2C%20was%20ill%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20under%20treatment%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20City%20Palace%20in%20Udaipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharana-prataps-descendant-royal-family-member-arvind-singh-mewar-dies-7934593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20launches%20wave%20of%20air%20strikes%20on%20Yemen's%20Houthis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742108742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F41e8%2Flive%2F6c131900-01d8-11f0-beca-4dfaec3846c2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc05mvr3j3yro%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Houthi-run%20health%20ministry%20says%2031%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20strikes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1224%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc05mvr3j3yro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc05mvr3j3yro.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%