e%20deportations%20for%20two%20weeks%20and%20set%20a%20Friday%20hearing%20to%20review%20legal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act%20is%20a%20United%20States%20federal%20law%20enacted%20in%201798%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Alien%20and%20Sedition%20Acts.%20This%20legislation%20grants%20the%20President%20authority%20to%20detain%20or%20deport%20non-citizens%20from%20nations%20considered%20hostile%20during%20times%20of%20declared%20war%20or%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProvisions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20declared%20war%2C%20the%20president%20can%20order%20the%20apprehension%2C%20restraint%2C%20and%20removal%20of%20citizens%20aged%2014%20and%20older%20from%20enemy%20nations%20residing%20in%20the%20US%2C%20based%20solely%20on%20their%20nationality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20allows%20these%20actions%20without%20the%20need%20for%20a%20court%20hearing%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20potential%20violations%20of%20constitutional%20rights%20such%20as%20due%20process%20and%20equal%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20act%20was%20introduced%20amid%20escalating%20tensions%20with%20France%20in%20the%20late%2018th%20century%2C%20aiming%20to%20prevent%20espionage%20and%20sabotage%20by%20foreign%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20James%20Madison%20applied%20the%20act%20for%20the%20first%20time%20during%20the%20War%20of%201812%2C%20to%20British%20nationals%20residing%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20World%20War%20I%2C%20the%20act%20facilitated%20the%20detention%20and%20deportation%20of%20individuals%20from%20enemy%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20World%20war%2C%20the%20act%20was%20invoked%20to%20authorise%20the%20internment%20of%20Japanese%2C%20German%2C%20and%20Italian%20nationals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Japanese-American%20citizens%2C%20a%20decision%20now%20widely%20criticised%20for%20violating%20civil%20liberties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20the%20President%20Use%20the%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act%20Without%20a%20Literal%20Invasion%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20terms%20like%20invasion%20and%20predatory%20incursion%20were%20understood%20literally%20--%20referring%20to%20large-scale%20attacks%20or%20smaller%20military%20raids.%20Some%20politicians%20now%20argue%20for%20a%20broader%20reading%2C%20suggesting%20that%20unlawful%20migration%20or%20drug%20trafficking%20qualifies%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binvasion.%26quot%3B%20They%20see%20the%20law%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20enforce%20mass%20deportations.%20Past%20courts%20and%20presidents%20have%20consistently%20treated%20it%20as%20a%20wartime%20authority%2C%20not%20an%20immigration%20enforcement%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Donald%20Trump%20Invoked%20The%20Act%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20Friday%2C%20the%20ACLU%20and%20Democracy%20Forward%20sued%20Trump's%20administration%2C%20arguing%20that%20five%20Venezuelan%20men%20were%20at%20%26quot%3Bimminent%20risk%26quot%3B%20of%20being%20deported%20under%20the%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act.%20Federal%20judge%2C%20James%20Boasberg%2C%20blocked%20their%20deportation%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20immediate%20appeal%20from%20the%20Justice%20Department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20struck%20a%20%246%20million%20deal%20with%20El%20Salvador%20to%20imprison%20300%20suspected%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang%20members.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Trump%20declared%20the%20gang%20an%20invading%20force%2C%20invoking%20wartime%20powers%20to%20justify%20mass%20deportations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20A%20President%20Invoke%20It%20in%20Peacetime%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegally%2C%20it%20would%20be%20an%20abuse%20of%20power.%20But%20the%20political%20question%20doctrine%20-%20which%20prevents%20courts%20from%20interfering%20in%20executive%20decisions%20on%20war%20and%20foreign%20policy%20-%20could%20limit%20judicial%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742106900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fod7s9lk8_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_07_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-what-is-alien-enemies-act-us-law-used-for-first-time-since-world-war-ii-7934174%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Saturday%20invoked%20the%20Alien%20Enemies%20Act%20-%20a%20wartime%20law%20last%20used%20in%20World%20War%20II%20-%20to%20deport%20individuals%20linked%20to%20Venezuela's%20Tren%20de%20Aragua%20gang.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20use%20of%20the%20act%20since%20World%20War%20II.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-what-is-alien-enemies-act-us-law-used-for-first-time-since-world-war-ii-7934174%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20electric%20two-wheeler%20launches%20drive%20market%20growth%20despite%20subsidy%20cuts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742106721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fnew-electric-two-wheeler-launches-drive-market-growth-despite-subsidy-cuts-125031600183_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Segment%20sees%20growth%20despite%20subsidy%20cuts%3B%20major%20OEMs%20expand%20portfolios%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20AR%20Rahman%20Discharged%20From%20Hospital%20-%20%26quot%3BHe%20Is%20Absolutely%20Fine%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOscar-winning%20music%20composer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fexclusive-ar-rahman-hospitalised-due-to-de