The%20410-meter-long%20Hyperloop%20test%20tube%20located%20at%20IIT%20Chennai%20is%20already%20the%20longest%20Hyperloop%20test%20facility%20in%20Asia.%20Hyperloop%20is%20a%20high-speed%20train%20that%20runs%20in%20a%20vacuum%20in%20a%20tube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20on%20Sunday%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BLongest%20Hyperloop%20tube%20in%20Asia%20(410%20m)...%20soon%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20longest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2015%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20visited%20the%20Hyperloop%20testing%20facility%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20Discovery%20Campus%20and%20witnessed%20a%20live%20demonstration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20journalists%2C%20the%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20entire%20testing%20system%20for%20Hyperloop%20transportation%20has%20been%20developed%20using%20indigenous%20technologies%2C%20and%20he%20congratulated%20all%20the%20young%20innovators%20for%20this%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20India%20will%20soon%20be%20ready%20for%20Hyperloop%20transportation%2C%20as%20the%20Hyperloop%20transportation%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20under%20development%2C%20has%20yielded%20good%20results%20in%20the%20tests%20conducted%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Ministry%20has%20been%20provided%20financial%20funding%20and%20technical%20assistance%20to%20the%20Hyperloop%20project%2C%20and%20now%2C%20all%20the%20electronics%20technology%20for%20this%20Hyperloop%20project%20will%20be%20developed%20at%20ICF%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20stated%20that%20highly%20skilled%20experts%20at%20the%20ICF%20factory%20have%20successfully%20developed%20larhe%20electronics%20systems%20for%20Vande%20Bharat%20high-speed%20trains%2C%20and%20the%20electronics%20technology%20for%20this%20Hyperloop%20project%20will%20also%20be%20developed%20at%20ICF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20congratulated%20the%20young%20innovators%20team%20of%20IIT%20Chennai%20and%20the%20Avishkar%20organization%20for%20this%20successful%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20Minister%20visited%20the%20IIT%20Chennai%20campus%20in%20Guindy%2C%20where%20he%20inspected%20the%20exhibition%20organized%20by%20the%20IIT's%20Center%20for%20Innovation%20titled%20Open%20House%202025.%20He%20interacted%20with%20students%20and%20young%20innovators.%20During%20the%20interaction%2C%20he%20stated%20that%20India%20will%20become%20a%20leading%20country%20in%20all%20sectors%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20noted%20that%20the%20youth%20are%20performing%20efficiently%20in%20the%20fields%20of%20data%20science%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20that%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20skilled%20youth%20in%20the%20world%2C%20who%20will%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20making%20India%20a%20developed%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20announced%20that%20presently%20there%20are%20five%20semiconductor%20facilities%20operational%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20first%20India%20made%20semiconductor%20will%20be%20rolled%20out%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20presented%20prizes%20and%20shields%20to%20the%20winners%20of%20the%20innovation%20competition%20held%20during%20the%20exhibition%20and%20encouraged%20them%20to%20create%20more%20new%20inventions.%20Dr.%20Kamakoti%2C%20Director%20of%20IIT%20Chennai%2C%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742105580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ficdphlg8_hyperloop_625x300_16_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%